User & Server

1. User -> Server
   * login/logoff
   *status

2. Server -> User
   * online/offline

3. User -> User
   *direct message
   *group message / broadcast


Commands : 
  login <userID> <password>
  logoff
  
  msg <user> body...

  #topic <-- chatroom/group chat
  join #topic
  leave #topic
  send:msg #topic body..
  recv:msg #topic-sender body..